<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l4">Mawrer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener / als von des Edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ des von <expan>Abenſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l5">wegen / 
<del rend="strikethrough">an ewr gnade </del> Vnd biten <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l6">fleıſʒ / 
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ Jr </del> vvaʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıener cʒu diſem male 
<del rend="strikethrough"> von </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_148_line_1572505115792_87">in </ab></add> der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l7"><expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache an ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> werb von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen / daʒ Jr Jn darynn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l8"><expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> / Jm des <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd 
