</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_148" id="74r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Bayern etc. </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir senden <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        aber czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> Hansen Mawrer,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, als von des edeln
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des von
                            <expan>Abensp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> wegen und biten
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, waz der
                            <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener czu disem male <add>in</add> der
                                <expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache an ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> werb von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen, daz ir in darynn
                                <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören,</expan> im des <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und <add>im</add> auch darynne durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> willigen
                        dinste <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> tun wöllet, als wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> des wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
